edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap
Class ProtegeSlotItem

java.lang.Object
  edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap.DMAPItem
      edu.uchsc.ccp.dmap.ProtegeSlotItem

public class ProtegeSlotItem
extends DMAPItem

This class represents a Protege Slot. DMAP is never looking for this slot directly, it looks up the frame constraints on this slot and then looks for compatible fillers.

Author:
Will Fitzgerald, R. James Firby
